><br />\nShit is all good. Last time I had this big ass dude next to me, his mama was huge as well but that wasn't the point. Why are we talking in English?"},{"pid":"ad55c334344209b1b37f14b5a20b937529128af4","tid":176124,"uid":80042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Air Canada is just another glorified mediocre North American airline. Or em, in other words if you think Cathay Pacific airways are crap then don't bother flying Air Canada at all. <br />\nspeaking of 6 years of Flying air Canada experience</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHow about sharing some of your flying experience in practical? Say seats comments or service experience</blockquote><br />\nShit is all good. Last time I had this big ass dude next to me, his mama was huge as well but that wasn't the point. Why are we talking in English?</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n禮貌黎架者<br />\n巴打用英文我又用英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75b166f6322c58fd200c0b300b4e4616850826e","tid":176124,"uid":25152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:03:18.000Z","msg":"搭完AC你會改變你個世界觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來呢個世界上真係有野食（飛機餐）難食過屎"},{"pid":"b605154973f5e09ff4fdc0cb87234f57e82ce618","tid":176124,"uid":80042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭完AC你會改變你個世界觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s